        <Summary xml:lang="en">Profanity - A console based XMPP client</Summary>
        <Description xml:lang="en">Profanity is a console based XMPP client written in C using ncurses and libstrophe, inspired by Irssi.
Feautres:
- Supports XMPP chat services, including GoogleTalk
- MUC chat room support
- OTR and PGP encryption
- Roster management
- Flexible resource and priority settings
- Desktop notifications
- Plugins in Python and C
</Description>
